<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Contriver" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Contriver,</orth> schemer, plotter: <cit><quote>we shall find of him a shrewd c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 2.1.158" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. II, 1, 158</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a secret and villanous c. against me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.1.151" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 1, 151</bibl></cit>. <emph>the damned c. of</emph> <cit><quote>this deed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 4.1.36" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 1, 36</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the close c. of all harms,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 3.5.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. III, 5, 7</bibl></cit>.
